    c) Add to the ios dependencies: compile "com.mobidevelop.robovm:robopods-google-mobile-ads-ios:$robopodsVersion"
    d) Download the Admob iOS library, and put the 'GoogleMobileAds.framework' into a new folder in the iOS project called 'libs'
